window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In this, the final book in C.S. Lewis's acclaimed Space Trilogy, which includes <i>Out of the Silent Planet</i> and <i>Perelandra</i>, <i>That Hideous Strength</i> concludes the adventures of the matchless Dr. Ransom. Finding himself in a world of superior alien beings and scientific experiments run amok, Dr. Ransom struggles with questions of ethics and morality, applying age-old wisdom to a brave new universe dominated by science. His quest for truth is a journey filled with intrigue and suspense.</p>"; 
